{"tid":2498314,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"小摩：如果比特幣不能很快重返60000美元以上水平，動能信號將會崩塌","createTime":"2021-04-21T05:32:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T05:49:01.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"818bbd4e2afd761900cb53d099201cfbcc98f1c1","tid":2498314,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"摩根大通報告稱，如果比特幣不能很快重返60,000美元以上水平，動能信號將會崩塌。<br />\n分析師表示，近幾周的比特幣期貨多頭加倉以及過去幾日的多頭平倉可能與商品交易顧問(CTA)和加密貨幣基金至少有一定的牽連。<br />\n「過去幾天比特幣期貨市場出現了與2月中旬、1月中旬和去年11月底類似的大規模平倉情形，」策略師們説。「鑑於其當前依然高企的水平，動能信號將會由此出現連續數月的衰減。」"},{"pid":"e86a6764fae79bf0db4bc49aa925d42f818b8ff6","tid":2498314,"uid":23127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"狗狗從後追上，取得冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f4843b2766dca424470fb49cab4c62ec573afb","tid":2498314,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"ETH<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bca61ef6ca2594ed088657d01892d5fadca0ead","tid":2498314,"uid":84926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86a6764fae79bf0db4bc49aa925d42f818b8ff6","tid":2498314,"uid":23127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"狗狗從後追上，取得冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:43:24.000Z","msg":"狗幣上60000<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013930eb107f27253e2d089765d3b325de71c0ca","tid":2498314,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T05:46:58.000Z","msg":"做空公司又想製造恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc35f954bddedaec0d824c0fcf11d777de9dbf5","tid":2498314,"uid":23127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"013930eb107f27253e2d089765d3b325